&lt;h2&gt;課程心得&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;variable的使用可簡化繪圖流程,像是如果有很多的尺寸因為變數需要更改,就可利用variable的功能一次性的修改。&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="2018Fall"></category></entry><entry><title>Week4</title><link href="https://mdecadp2018.github.io/site-40623142/blog/4.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2018-10-05T11:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2018-10-05T11:00:00+08:00</updated><author><name>40623142</name></author><id>tag:mdecadp2018.github.io,2018-10-05:/site-40623142/blog/4.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Week4 Onshape&lt;/p&gt;
